Description:Test puzzle for replaying a persist loop: Kitchen Finks plus Vizier of Remedies plus Goblin Bombardment and Zulaport Cutthroat. Record one cycle that sacrifices Kitchen Finks to Goblin Bombardment targeting the opponent, lets persist return Kitchen Finks without a -1/-1 counter, and lets the drain and life-gain triggers resolve. Repeat until the opponent is defeated.

